IMAPAccount gmail
    Host imap.gmail.com
    User andy.dirnberger@gmail.com
    PassCmd "security find-internet-password -s 'smtp.gmail.com' -a 'andy.dirnberger@gmail.com' -w"
    SSLType IMAPS
    SSLVersion TLSv1.2
    AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore gmail-remote
    Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
    Path ~/Mail/gmail/
    Inbox ~/Mail/gmail/Inbox
    Subfolders Verbatim

Channel gmail
    Master :gmail-remote:
    Slave :gmail-local:
    Patterns *
    Create Both
    Remove Both
    SyncState *

